data.description: This charming home boasts 4 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms, 2 separate Living Areas as well as an Office! NEW Boiler! NEW Water Heater! Situated on a LARGE Corner Lot; with room to expand, build a shop/RV Garage or add your personal touch. Small town living at its finest, come see what Limon has to offer! within walking distance to the NEWLY CONSTRUCTED community pool as well as the K-12 school! Away from the hustle and bustle of the city; you will get that country life feel while still being part of a great community. Everything you need within walking distance or take the RZR, 4-wheeler or even your tractor around town.
